rows.label: tlk45320122_01_msg0001
rows.name:
When I was first dispatched to Torigo,
I thought it would be a nice, peaceful
city where the days roll by.

rows.label: tlk45320122_01_msg0002
rows.name:
But it seems like a lot of
the Gulans still bear a
grudge against Superbia...

rows.label: tlk45320122_01_msg0003
rows.name:
And the other day, we even had
unauthorized Drivers infiltrating
our base! Unbelievable...

rows.label: tlk45320122_01_msg0004
rows.name:
There's no end to our troubles
here, I'm telling you.

rows.label: tlk45320122_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Still, it's a far sight better
than the home country. Even if
we are short of a consul...
